{
  "stem": "27340.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They lived in a hospital, in the basement of a hospital and so on, together with hundreds of other people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had a very uncomfortable life during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they tried to stick to London as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I finished my school at the age of 14, I had to look for a job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was very, very fortunate to be offered an apprenticeship as a tool maker in a tool making company in-- in Walsall in Staffordshire.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I started work there-- we worked there, excuse me, we worked there for the 12-hour-- 12-hour shifts, two weeks on days and two weeks on nights.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think I gained a-- a tremendous experience which later on in my career development as an engineer stood me in very, very good standing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- this started in 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, we were granted-- each war worker was granted-- one week's holiday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was always very interested in plants and agriculture and natural things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so a friend of mine, also a refugee from Breslau who served an apprenticeship as a-- as an industrial chemist in Birmingham, we decided to go to a camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We decided to go and dig for victory, and the easiest way of doing that was to attach oneself to a youth camp of which there were quite a lot of those in those days.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it's appropriate to say here that for about a year I'd been toying with the idea of what, in fact, did Judaism offer me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'd suffered tremendously.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The family was torn to bits and pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK, the four of us were still together in the UK in relative safety.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
